# Peresvet Frontend and Configurator Rules

- Keep Grafana Configurator behavior aligned with backend model and API contracts.
- Preserve existing saved model/dashboard compatibility unless the task explicitly changes persisted structure.
- Keep create, edit, delete and display flows consistent for affected entities.
- Validate required fields, defaults, enum values and nested model structures before sending requests.
- Surface backend errors in a useful operator-facing way.
- Do not mix unrelated dashboard cleanup with feature work.
- Document manual Grafana-dependent checks when they cannot be run.
